e B has reliability and calmness but negative teamwork. Candidate C has conscientiousness (reliability) and quick decisions, but communication difficulty and egocentric. Candidate D has responsibility and problem solving, but hot temper and know-it-all, no calmness data. So B still seems strongest for safety-critical aspects. So we can vote Candidate B.\n\nWe must output PUBLIC_MESSAGE with our contribution: answer the two questions, maybe give brief assessment, and vote.\n\nMake sure to follow format: PUBLIC_MESSAGE: <text> then METADATA_JSON with agent \"agent_1\" and vote.\n\nLet's craft."}
